rows.label: tlk45600551_03_msg0001
rows.name:
The Superbian economy seems to have
really picked up lately.

rows.label: tlk45600551_03_msg0002
rows.name:
You can get things for cheaper than
before, and new products are starting
to become available.

rows.label: tlk45600551_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I guess that's thanks to consumers
buying plenty of stuff, and people's
problems getting sorted out.

rows.label: tlk45600551_03_msg0004
rows.name:
When people's lives are happier, they
spend more freely, which is good for
keeping the economy moving.
